<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="3.8.5">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://incarceratedwombats.com/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="https://incarceratedwombats.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2019-08-22T11:49:09+00:00</updated><id>https://incarceratedwombats.com/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Incarcerated Wombats</title><subtitle>Incarcerated Wombats is a hard rock band from the Long Island, New York area mostly active from 2008-2014.</subtitle><entry><title type="html">Practice on 21 August 2019</title><link href="https://incarceratedwombats.com/practices/2019/08/22/practice-on-21-august-2019.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Practice on 21 August 2019" /><published>2019-08-22T11:31:30+00:00</published><updated>2019-08-22T11:31:30+00:00</updated><id>https://incarceratedwombats.com/practices/2019/08/22/practice-on-21-august-2019</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://incarceratedwombats.com/practices/2019/08/22/practice-on-21-august-2019.html">&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/pQyqoefMgb4?rel=0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;allowfullscreen&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Practice on 6 August 2019</title><link href="https://incarceratedwombats.com/practices/2019/08/10/practice-on-6-august-2019.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Practice on 6 August 2019" /><published>2019-08-10T06:21:00+00:00</published><updated>2019-08-10T06:21:00+00:00</updated><id>https://incarceratedwombats.com/practices/2019/08/10/practice-on-6-august-2019</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://incarceratedwombats.com/practices/2019/08/10/practice-on-6-august-2019.html">&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/620fexWqEz0?rel=0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;allowfullscreen&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">The wombat returns!</title><link href="https://incarceratedwombats.com/posts/2019/07/31/the-wombat-returns.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="The wombat returns!" /><published>2019-07-31T11:20:00+00:00</published><updated>2019-07-31T11:20:00+00:00</updated><id>https://incarceratedwombats.com/posts/2019/07/31/the-wombat-returns</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://incarceratedwombats.com/posts/2019/07/31/the-wombat-returns.html">&lt;p&gt;Our lead guitarist has returned - huzzah! Should be practicing weekly again.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/VX5REW1Pd-Y?rel=0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;allowfullscreen&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><category term="posts" /><summary type="html">Our lead guitarist has returned - huzzah! Should be practicing weekly again.</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Calling all wombats…</title><link href="https://incarceratedwombats.com/posts/2019/03/24/calling-all-wombats.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Calling all wombats..." /><published>2019-03-24T12:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2019-03-24T12:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://incarceratedwombats.com/posts/2019/03/24/calling-all-wombats</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://incarceratedwombats.com/posts/2019/03/24/calling-all-wombats.html">&lt;p&gt;We’re trying to get back into the game and decided to test out our old instruments and attempt some of our songs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Just waiting on our lead guitarist now. Come back to the warm embrace of the wombat!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/deR-s2gGDdU?rel=0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;allowfullscreen&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><category term="posts" /><summary type="html">We’re trying to get back into the game and decided to test out our old instruments and attempt some of our songs.</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Website refreshed</title><link href="https://incarceratedwombats.com/posts/2019/03/20/website-refreshed.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Website refreshed" /><published>2019-03-20T12:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2019-03-20T12:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://incarceratedwombats.com/posts/2019/03/20/website-refreshed</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://incarceratedwombats.com/posts/2019/03/20/website-refreshed.html">&lt;p&gt;Hello, long lost wombats.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is a long due update. The website has been refreshed and all of our recordings (video &amp;amp; audio) are now hosted on YouTube. Now long after we’re all dead our legacy will live on so others may follow the wombat.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We’re all feeling nostalgic for the days when we would practice every week. Perhaps something will come together and we will all return to the warm embrace of the wombat.&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><category term="posts" /><summary type="html">Hello, long lost wombats.</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Website updated</title><link href="https://incarceratedwombats.com/posts/2015/06/01/website-updated.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Website updated" /><published>2015-06-01T13:59:01+00:00</published><updated>2015-06-01T13:59:01+00:00</updated><id>https://incarceratedwombats.com/posts/2015/06/01/website-updated</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://incarceratedwombats.com/posts/2015/06/01/website-updated.html">&lt;p&gt;Hello fellow wombats!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The videos page has been removed and now we have a &lt;a href=&quot;/practices&quot;&gt;Practices&lt;/a&gt; page that includes all of those videos along with all of our older audio-only recordings.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I also did some digging and found recordings from way back in 2008! You’ll also find two videos from 2009 have been added along with two videos from October 5, 2012. I should also be putting up one more from Febuary 1, 2012 soon. After that we should be all caught up. It will be really cool to have everything ever recorded on the website.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hopefully our guitarist will turn up again and we’ll be able to jam together.&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><category term="posts" /><summary type="html">Hello fellow wombats!</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Practice on 21 June 2014</title><link href="https://incarceratedwombats.com/practices/2014/06/21/practice-on-21-june-2014.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Practice on 21 June 2014" /><published>2014-06-21T12:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2014-06-21T12:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://incarceratedwombats.com/practices/2014/06/21/practice-on-21-june-2014</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://incarceratedwombats.com/practices/2014/06/21/practice-on-21-june-2014.html">&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/j-79EohNMN0?rel=0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;allowfullscreen&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Practice on 26 April 2014</title><link href="https://incarceratedwombats.com/practices/2014/04/26/practice-on-26-april-2014.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Practice on 26 April 2014" /><published>2014-04-26T12:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2014-04-26T12:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://incarceratedwombats.com/practices/2014/04/26/practice-on-26-april-2014</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://incarceratedwombats.com/practices/2014/04/26/practice-on-26-april-2014.html">&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/JXyHoM_SNKQ?rel=0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;allowfullscreen&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Practice on 27 July 2013</title><link href="https://incarceratedwombats.com/practices/2013/07/27/practice-on-27-july-2013.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Practice on 27 July 2013" /><published>2013-07-27T12:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2013-07-27T12:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://incarceratedwombats.com/practices/2013/07/27/practice-on-27-july-2013</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://incarceratedwombats.com/practices/2013/07/27/practice-on-27-july-2013.html">&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/mjvsPjs9fEI?rel=0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;allowfullscreen&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Website updated</title><link href="https://incarceratedwombats.com/posts/2013/07/24/website-updated.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Website updated" /><published>2013-07-24T17:19:46+00:00</published><updated>2013-07-24T17:19:46+00:00</updated><id>https://incarceratedwombats.com/posts/2013/07/24/website-updated</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://incarceratedwombats.com/posts/2013/07/24/website-updated.html">&lt;p&gt;Hey everybody - just want to write a quick post about some new features and fixes on the website.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We’ve added a link to our new Google+ page on the home page and we now have our RSS feed working. If you have an RSS reader you can subscribe to our new posts! We’ve also updated the videos page to only show five videos per page. There are also a bunch of minor fixes that should make using the website easier. Hope you enjoy the updates!&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><category term="posts" /><summary type="html">Hey everybody - just want to write a quick post about some new features and fixes on the website.</summary></entry></feed>